            <title>[HBASE-3907] make it easier to add per-CF metrics; add some key per-CF metrics to start with</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3907</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add plumbing needed to add various types of per ColumnFamily metrics. And to start with add a bunch per-CF metrics such as:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) Blocks read, cache hit, avg time of read for a column family.&lt;br/&gt;
2) Similar stats for compaction related reads.&lt;br/&gt;
3) Stats for meta block reads per CF&lt;br/&gt;
4) Bloom Filter stats per CF&lt;br/&gt;
etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
