                            <comment id="13450720" author="kannanm" created="Fri, 7 Sep 2012 15:27:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is all done from a while ago, and ported to trunk as well. The port might have happened as part of the HFile V2 port. So I don&apos;t have the exact patch details. But we pretty much have block cache stats, compaction stats, bloom/index/ stats on a per-CF, get/put ops/latency stats, on a per-CF basis.&lt;/p&gt;

